project.name: ROU HR Data Warehouse
project.description:
HR Data Warehouse project objective is to define the single point of truth for HR reporting within A&D Pharma that includes key processes, tools, infrastructure and reports review, improvement, and automation.

Currently, the monthly reporting is taking too long, is partially automated and the required data comes from different sources: Charisma HR, reports, manual adjustments in excel, etc. This situation generates high efforts to administer, report and reconcile the data with negative impact on decision making process.

HR Data Mart project objectives are structured as follows:

Create the HR Data Warehouse as single source of truth for monthly and ad-hoc reporting and automated creation of monthly reports
Implement the presentation layer based on PowerBI Identify and select the presentation layer tool (i.e. PowerBI) to be used in HR Cost Controlling Team, as business owner, in order to increase flexibility and independence in reporting activities with much lower independence dependence towards IT BI 
Development and Implementation of advanced Management Dashboards that will allow an interactive presentation of the HR related KPI’s
